Description: fcmconfr streamlines the process of conducting dynamic simulations 
  using Fuzzy Cognitive Maps (FCMs). The package supports multiple FCM types 
  (conventional, Interval-Value Fuzzy Number (IVFN) and Triangular Fuzzy Number 
  (TFN)) and provides tools for model aggregation and the propagation of 
  uncertainty from individual FCMs through to the aggregate.
